### Production API Tests
### Base URL
@baseUrl = https://localhost:7189
@connectionId = your-connection-id-here
@token = your-jwt-token-here

###############################################################################
# ENHANCED CONNECTION TESTING
###############################################################################

### 1. Enhanced Connection Test (with Qdrant check + auto indexing)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/connections/{{connectionId}}/test-enhanced
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

# This API will:
# - Test database connection
# - Check if Qdrant collection exists
# - Auto-index schemas if collection is empty
# - Return readyForChat status

###############################################################################
# AGENT MESSAGE PROCESSING
###############################################################################

### 2. Process Message with Agent (Production)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/agent/process
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "connectionId": "{{connectionId}}",
  "question": "Show me all customers"
}

### 3. Process Message - Complex Query
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/agent/process
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "connectionId": "{{connectionId}}",
  "question": "Show me top 5 customers by total spent with their order count"
}

### 4. Process Message - With Conversation Context
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/agent/process
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "connectionId": "{{connectionId}}",
  "question": "What about their recent orders?",
  "conversationId": "existing-conversation-id"
}

###############################################################################
# COMPARISON WITH TEST ENDPOINTS
###############################################################################

### 5. Test Controller - Process Query (Test Only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/test/process-query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Show me all customers"
}

# Note: This uses hardcoded test database (TextToSqlTest)
# While /api/agent/process uses user's actual connections

